question: Koa lō͘ siâu chòe cē chiah ū chhùnn chhut chòe chē pō· ê tiān-sī-kio̍k ê miâ, sī tan-to̍k siá-chok ia̍h-sī chiâⁿ-chòe chi̍t ê tūi-ngó· ê chi̍t ê chok-ka?
Tī lia̍t-chhut ê hāng-bo̍k lāi-té, ū kúi-ê sī chi̍t-ê tū-chāi ê saⁿ ūi chok-ka siá ê?
Tī chiah chi̍t ê chhut-phín ê khai-sí liân-pò ê ji̍t-kî sī jīm-hô? Chiah ê chhut-phín sī hō͘ siá chò "Who's the Boss?" ê tūi ê sêng-oân siá--ê?
1991 ni mi̍h goe̍h ê chhut-liân phah-chhut ê hong-sek chhai̍ⁿ ch likeⁿ? I sī tiāⁿ-tiāⁿ bô tiāⁿ-tiāⁿ, chi̍t-ē chin-chiáⁿ ê sū sī siáⁿ-mi̍h?
answer: 1991 nî 11 goe̍h ê chhut-liân hong-sek chin tiāⁿ-tiāⁿ. Ta̍k-ê ti̍t-sì thiaⁿ-chhut ê ê ji̍t-kî sī 11/2, 11/9, 11/16, chi̍t-ê 11/23. In ê ji̍t-kî sī keh chheⁿ chi̍t léng, chiáⁿ-mi̍h sī kóng i sī chi̍t-ê chiāⁿ-tiāⁿ ê léng-léng chhut-liân hō͘-sìn, chiàⁿ-mi̍h sī leh ián-kè sī léng-léng chhut-liân (bá-jit).

question: Sioh chiong 1992 nî tio̍h chhut-liân ê, iáu-ū chi̍t-ê lâng siá ê ti̍t-chhit ê miâ-jī. , chiong 1992 nî tio̍h chhut-liân ê, iáu-ū chi̍t-ê lâng siá ê ti̍t-chhit ê miâ-jī.
answer: Tony Micelli, This is Your Other Life

question: Tī chhú khòaⁿ ê choân-pō͘ lū-hō͘ lāi-bīn, ū kúi-ê cha̍p-hun-chi It ê choân-pō͘ ê iáⁿ-phìⁿ sī chi̍t-ê nn̄g ê lâng ê tūi siá ê?
Nāi-su̍t sî-lia̍t ê "Misery" ài khì hō͘ "Death and Love (Part 1)" ê tâng-lâng siá, ná-tiāⁿ chi̍t kóa lóng sī "Bob Rosenfarb, Danny Kallis & Phil Doran" tâng-lâng siá ê phìn-tō͘ ū kúi-ê?
Tī chiah-ê chhut-miâ chheh lāi-bīn, ū bô ū chi̍t-ê siá chheh ê tūi-ngó͘ ū hō͘ phài chòe liân-sòa ê hāng-bo̍k ê chi̍t-pō͘-hūn? chhiáⁿ chiàu chū-liāu lâi kái-soeh lí ê koan-î.
answer: Ū, chiàu ū-tāi ê chū-liāu lâi kóng, ū chin bêng-hián ê chha-pia̍t. Kū-iú ê chhut-miâ chheh ê tan-it tō sī 'Ai-chêng kah Sì-bông' ('Death and Love'), 'Tē-it chi̍p' ('Part 1') kah 'Tē-jī chi̍p' ('Part 2') lóng sī kā chi̍t ê siá chheh ê tūi-ngó͘: 'Bob Rosenfarb, Danny Kallis & Phil Doran'. Chiah ê chē-chē chiâⁿ-bêng chòe chòe chāi-sū kah gí-tâi ê tūi-hōe.

question: Tī si sann-ê sò͘-ba̍t lia̍t-toa̍h ū hō͘-chè biâu chheng-chhò͘ ê tāi-bé, i ê lōe-iông hō͘-chè sī to̍k-it ê, tān-sī chhián-liam kah chha-khì ê lia̍t-chhut, chheng-chhò͘ kóng boán-choân ê choan-chi̍p ê lōe-iông bōe-tiāu liat chāi?
Tōa-su, chāi só͘-chāi ê piáu-ta̍t lāi-té, chūi-chūi chio̍h-chāi ê kò͘-chè sî-kan kái-tò ê tē-it chi̍p ê phiau-tē sī ūi-chāi?
answer: Tony, Can You Spare a Dime?

question: Tī 1991 nî 10 goe̍h 12 ji̍t tē 11 pái khong-phòaⁿ ê sī sī hō-chòe ūi?
